      policy in the asymptomatic patient, or with single agent treatments with the purpose of
      maintaining a good quality of life for a prolonged time.The combination of rituximab and
      ibrutinib has been tested in clinical trials and appeared to be well tolerated and active.
      Since ibrutinib seems to achieve better results when administered for prolonged time as shown
